Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:08.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's obvious. We will bet everything on the line and gamble.}Dĩ nhiên là...đặt cược tất cả vào cờ bạc rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.2,554.4)}{About yesterday. Were you serious?}Chuyện hôm qua...cậu nghiêm túc hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,564)}{You challenged the student council president.}Đối thủ là Hội trưởng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:23.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You do understand how serious this is, right?}Cậu biết mình đang làm gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:23.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:27.83,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're worried about me. I really appreciate it.}Cám ơn vì đã lo cho tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:31.80,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. But I will not change my decision.}Nhưng tớ sẽ không đổi ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:37.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I just couldn't resist that juicy challenge.}Sao có thể từ chối cơ chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to stop you.}Tớ không ngăn cậu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:44.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I want to be with you when you gamble.}Chỉ là muốn ở bên cạnh cậu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:45.67,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}Ồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I want to show it to Yumeko.}Tớ muốn cho Yumeko thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:56.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You guys, why are you so calm?\NSince you have time for chit-chat, how about we talk strategy?}Hai người rảnh nhỉ? Thế bàn chiến thuật đến đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.03,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Strategy?}Chiến thuật?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.45,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You decided to gamble with the president, isn't that right?}Chiến thuật đấu với Hội trưởng?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{For starters a special dice.\NYou can roll the numbers you need with it.}Đầu tiên là xúc xắc có thể chọn mặt tùy ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:16.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I have six of them in different colors.}Em có 6 con với 6 màu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.85,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Next we have infrared cards.}Tiếp theo là bộ bài này.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:24.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you look at them through an infrared camera,\Nyou'll be able to see which card is which.}Nếu có kính hồng ngoại, có thể biết rõ những lá bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.13,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And finally my favorite one.}Và thứ em thích nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:32.46,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The trick here is simple but very effective.\NIt's called—}Đơn giản như hiệu quả, đây là--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:36.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hold on! Cheating? That's your strategy?}Khoan? Mấy cậu định gian lận à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.75,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This should be obvious even to you.}Hả? Cậu nói điều hiển nhiên thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's playing against the president.}Chúng ta đấu với Hội trưởng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.45,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This is the least we can do.}Nên bắt buộc phải chơi thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.79,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I appreciate your thoughtfulness.}Cám ơn mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.53,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I don't plan on cheating whatsoever.}Nhưng chị không định chơi xấu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.63,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Why is that?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:02:00.46,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Because I've always wanted to gamble with her, \N I don't want to ruin the game with cheating.}Vì không muốn phá hoại game bằng gian lận.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:01.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{W...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, I thought you'd be like that.}Biết ngay mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.97,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Seems like we have just have to go with this.}Chúng ta chỉ cần chuẩn bị tinh thần thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:10.31,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Seems like it...}Có lẽ vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:14.35,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Eh? You guys are coming along?}Hai người đi chung à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Of course. I told you that she made fun of me.}Dĩ nhiên. Cô ta dám coi thường tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I want to see her crash and burn with my own eyes.}Phải thấy ả bị hành hạ tôi mới vui được.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.45,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And I bet everything on you, Yumeko-senpai.}Em đặt cược vào chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui, Mary, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cám ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.37,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Welcome, everyone.}Chào mừng mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The president is waiting.}Chủ tịch đang chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:21.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This way, please.}Lối này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for coming.}Cám ơn vì đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for inviting me, Kirari-san.}Bọn tôi đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.97,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Let's skip the courtesy.}Bỏ qua màn chào hỏi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.92,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Shall we hurry up and begin?}Nhanh lên và bắt đầu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.43,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't think I can resist for much longer.}Tôi không chịu nổi nữa rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We can't just leave this treat hanging in front of everyone here.}Món ngon trước mắt thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:50.15,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ever since I saw you in this academy...\NAnd possibly even before this...}Từ khi vào học viện này...không, từ rất lâu rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.61,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I've been dreaming of this day for a long time.}Tớ đã mơ đến ngày hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Jabami Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:05:00.87,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.\NYou're attention please!}Rồi, rồi, rồi! Chú ý nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:07.58,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I, Yomozuki Runa, will be your judge!}Tôi, Yumozuki Runa sẽ là nhà cái!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:16.53,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's great that both of you are excited for the game.\NSo relax and leave everything to me!}Hãy tận hưởng và để mọi chuyện tôi lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:23.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{First let's talk about your bets. You said you're going \Nto bet everything. Do you have anything specific in mind?}Đầu tiên về khoan cược. Mọi thứ là sao nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:27.23,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko, are you having fun here?}Yumeko, ở đây cô thấy vui chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.65,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes, lots of fun. An academy where \Neverything is decided by gambling...}Rất vui. Một nơi quyết định mọi thứ bằng cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you win - it's heaven.\NIf you lose - it's hell.}Nếu thắng lên thường đường, thua xuống địa ngục.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{People live here by taking risks.}Lúc nào cũng sống trong rủi ro, lo sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's no other place like this.}Một nơi có một không hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.75,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hyakkaou Academy is the perfect place for me.}Là nơi lý tưởng của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.50,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you like it.}Thật vui khi cô thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:56.92,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The rules of the outside world don't have any power here.\NThe only rule here is gambling. It's survival of the fittest.}Luật bên ngoài chẳng là gì. Ở đây, cờ bạc là luật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:02.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This unique place where everyone is\Ndesperately trying to live on. I love this academy.}Đây là nơi mà chúng ta thực sự "sống". Tôi thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hyakkaou Academy is my personal aquarium.}Nơi này là bể cá của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:13.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's beautiful. You've put your heart and \N soul into this academy.}Thật tuyệt. Hội trưởng đặt cả trái tim vào nó nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:14.65,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This means...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.86,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:21.49,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The loser will never set foot in this academy again.}Kẻ thua sẽ không bao giờ được trở lại nơi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Do you agree to this?}Được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:23.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Không vấn đề.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.41,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{T-That's...}C-Chuyện này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:27.88,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yume—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:28.87,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{President!}Chủ tịch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Please reconsider it. That's too...}Xin hãy khoan đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.29,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hold on.}Chờ đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:40.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This makes no sense. You get nothing if you win. \N There's no point in participating.}Thế thắng chẳng được gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:45.01,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You think so? Do you gamble only if there's something to win?}Vậy sao? Cô nghĩ cờ bạc phải có kẻ thắng?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Maybe }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ do, yes.}Với cô có thể là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.77,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But for many others it's different.}Nhưng người khác thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{They live on on taking such gambles.}Họ "sống" với cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:03.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{They say humans are irrational creatures, but coming this far without a reason is rare.}Người ta thường nói con người là tạo bất thường, \Nnhưng có thể tồn tại đến bây giờ quả là hiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:09.79,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Gambling doesn't get them anything, they only lose something.}Cờ bạc không đem lại cho ta thứ gì mà nó chỉ lấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But even so, we still gamble.}Nhưng dù thế chúng ta vẫn cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We do that because we enjoy the risk.}Vì ai cũng thích sự rủi ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.53,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Runa, continue please.}Runa, tiếp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.43,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Aye-aye! Itsuki-chan, do you have Tarot cards?}Rõ! Itsuki, có mang bài Tarot không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Eh? Why do you ask?}Sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We'll use them for this game.}Chúng ta sẽ dùng nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:35.36,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We also have a deck here but you'll feel\Nbetter if we use your cards, right?}Ở đây cũng có nhưng xài của em thì an tâm hơn, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I have them...}Có nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:45.15,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And I removed card markings earlier \N because Yumeko told me to. What a waste!}Mình đã bỏ bộ có thể gian lận...Phí quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thank you!}Cám ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:50.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Now, I will explain the rules.}Giờ thì giải thích luật chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:57.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{For better or for worse, this bet will greatly change our fate.}Lần này sẽ quyết định đến vận mệnh của chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So let's do some fortune-telling.}Thế nên bói thử nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.00,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.88,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The name of the game is...}Tên của nó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{"Tarot cards of fate".}"Bài Tarot của định mệnh".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:09.11,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We will use twenty-two cards and play three rounds.}Chúng ta sẽ sử dụng 20 lá và chơi 3 vòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Each round only one of us will pick a card and turn it over.}Mỗi vòng chỉ một người được chọn và lật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:19.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Each card has a number from zero to twenty-one.\NThis number will determine your score.}Mỗi lá sẽ đánh số từ 1 đến 21. Và đó là số điểm đạt được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:25.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But if your card's position is upright, you get plus points.\NAnd if position is reversed, you get minus points.}Nhưng nếu lá bài bị ngược sẽ bị trừ điểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:30.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko wins if the sum of her cards is positive.}Yumeko sẽ thắng nếu giá trị bài dương điểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.58,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If it's negative then I win.}Còn âm điểm tôi thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.29,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{However...}Tuy nhiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:41.25,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's a special card. The Fool. \NThis card with zero points will be our Joker.}Có một lá mang số 0. Kẻ Khờ. Nó sẽ là lá Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:48.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If Yumeko picks this card and it's upright, she wins.\NIf I pick it and it's reversed, I win. Our scores won't matter.}Chỉ cần lấy được lá này thì auto thắng, \Nnhưng nếu bị lật ngược thì auto thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:55.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Our fate rests on this single card.\NIt can reverse any outcome.}Định mệnh của chúng ta sẽ được quyết định bởi nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Tarot cards can tell you the timing of something.}Bài Tarot có thể bói được số phận của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:07.37,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So the three cards that we pick will represent\Nthe past, the present and the future.}Ba lá chúng ta chọn sẽ đại diện cho quá khứ, hiện tại và tương lai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:12.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Let's see how did we end up here.}Hãy bói thử xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What's going to happen to us now.}Chuyện gì sẽ xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And what awaits us in the future.}Và thứ gì đang chờ đón ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.25,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Let the cards tell us our fate.}Hãy để những lá bài nói lên hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:25.72,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Okay! So who's going to pick the third card?}Rồi! Vậy ai sẽ là người chọn 3 lá bài?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:30.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, Yumeko will pick the present and \N I will pick the past. Let's go with that.}Yumeko sẽ chọn hiện tại còn tôi là quá khứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You... You're going with the past?}C-Chị chọn quá khứ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.85,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And for the future...}Và lá tương lai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.27,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You. What's your name?}Cậu. Tên?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{M-My name?}T-Tôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:52.70,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Very well, Ryota. You will be the one to pick the future.}Tốt, cậu sẽ là tương lai, Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.93,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Why me!?}Tại sao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:59.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's nice! Suzui-san, let's do our best!}Hay đấy Suzui! Hãy làm hết sức nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.38,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:05.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This might be my last chance to gamble in this academy.}Có thể đây sẽ là cơ hội cuối cùng của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko's last chance?}Cơ hội cuối?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:16.72,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If I lose this gamble then I'll leave this place. \N So I'd like you to help me out, Suzui-san.}Nếu thua, tớ sẽ rời khỏi đây. Nên ít nhất muốn được chơi với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't think I can do this much...}Mình không nghĩ xa đến thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.71,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Of course! All those times...}Đúng rồi! Từ ngày đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Alright.}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I will pick the future.}Tớ sẽ chọn tương lai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.70,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Everything's settled. So, shall we begin?}Xong rồi à? Bắt đầu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:42.15,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{These Tarot cards will tell us our fate.}Những lá bài Tarot bói vận mệnh của chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.14,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Everything is set!}Chuẩn bị hoàn thành!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:01.55,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We start with Yumeko-chan!\NTime to see the present.}Bắt đầu từ Yumeko! Hiện tại!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.10,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll pick this one.}Chọn lá này thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.51,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure about this one?}Chắc chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{'Kay! Show us your card!}Rồi! Mở bài!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:22.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There are only three rounds. The chance to get negative points is high.\NBut there's nothing you can do about it.}Chỉ có ba vòng. Cơ hội lấy điểm âm khá cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:29.05,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The Magician, position upright! \N Her score is now +1. }Ma pháp sư, không bị ngược! 1 điểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{O-Only plus one?}C-Chỉ 1 điểm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:37.93,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I guess it's a little low for a gamble\Nwith everything on the line.}Có vẻ hơi thấp nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:44.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No, this is fine. Since all the cards have an opposite,\Nthe expected points are between zero and ten.}Không, như thế là đủ. Vì bài trên bàn có thể mang giá trị âm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.90,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And she's got a positive one, so that's a win.}Chỉ cần được 1 điểm cũng là lợi thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:52.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yeees, we're getting there! Next one is the president!\NChoose your card, please!}Rồi! Tiếp theo là Hội trưởng! Quá khứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko, do you believe in destiny?}Yumeko, cô có tin vào vận mệnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Destiny?}Vận mệnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:05.21,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Destiny. When everything is decided from the very beginning.}Phải. Mọi thứ được quyết định ngay từ khi bắt đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.13,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If something like that exists, it would be very romantic.}Nếu có thứ như thế thì hẳn là lãng mạn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:19.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I think the same. It's unlikely that everything is decided from the beginning.\N But at the same time, I think that concept of destiny still exists.}Tôi cũng nghĩ thế. Tuy không chắc nhưng tôi nghĩ nó vẫn còn tồn tại.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:23.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{In roulette, do you know how many times in a row you can hit black?}Trong bàn Roulette, cô có biết mình có thể \Nvào ô màu đen bao nhiêu lần không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:30.36,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Twenty-seven times. The probability is quite high.}Là 27 lần. Xác suất khá cao nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I guess, the dealer that might see this would think something like...}Tôi nghĩ nhà cái hẳn cũng biết rõ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{"There's something wrong with this table".}"A, cái bàn này hỏng rồi".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:44.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Because if that was the case, then everyone\Nwould just hit black all the time.}Vì nếu không thế, mọi người ai cũng đặt vào ô màu đen mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:50.29,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Even if something seems impossible,\Nit doesn't mean it can't happen.}Dù điều đó là không thể nhưng không có nghĩa là nó không xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:55.80,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{When something like this happens, people attribute it to destiny.}Và khi đó mọi người lại bảo là vận mệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{In the end, we call these stories fate or destiny.}Cuối cùng, chúng ta làm quá lên và gọi nó là vận mệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:10.61,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko, how do you call this one, I wonder?}Yumeko, cô gọi cái này là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{A reversed one! World!}Đảo ngược! Lá Thế giới!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.77,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And the points...}Điểm số là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Minus twenty-one!}Âm 21!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:28.25,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Not bad, president! To pick such a card, you're really lucky! }Quả không hổ danh Hội trưởng! Thật may mắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:34.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No way... She got minus twenty-one just like that?}Đùa sao...Đạt điểm âm 21...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's cheating!}Là lừa đảo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:45.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Itsuki-chan. Didn't you hear what our president\Nwas talking about just mere moments ago?}Itsuki, không nghe Hội trưởng nói gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it!}Đừng lo lắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:58.32,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{My decisions are neutral and don't favor anyone!\NThe president did not cheat, I guarantee it.}Quyết định của tôi là công bằng. Đảm bảo không ai gian lận ở đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:05.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The current difference is twenty points.\N Are you ready, Suzui Ryouta-kun?}Hiện tại tỉ số đang là 1 và âm 21. Chuẩn bị chưa, Ryota?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:10.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You need to pick The Fool in the upright position \N if you want Yumeko to win.}Nếu muốn thắng phải lấy được lá Kẻ Khờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You know that, right?}Mà chắc cũng biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:21.35,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The Fool in order to win... \N Any hints where it might be...?}Lá bài đó...Có manh mối gì không nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:24.81,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I see it!}Không lẽ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:30.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hey now! Be quiet. Suzui-kun will choose the card himself.}Này này, im lặng. Để Suzui chọn bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:35.57,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This is a warning, so keep your advice to yourself. \N Talking to him is against the rules.}Đây là cảnh cáo đó. Không được nói chuyện riêng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.07,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So, Suzui-kun, tell us the future!}Rồi Suzui! Chọn {\s1}vợ {\s0}tương lai đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:47.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Twenty cards still remain. Only one of those is The Fool. \NI have to pick it and it has to be upright.}Một trong số chúng là Kẻ Khờ. Mình phải chọn chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:57.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The chances of this happening is one in twenty! \N I don't think I can do this.}Tỉ lệ 1/20! Mình không nghĩ có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:06.13,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Please do not worry that much about it.\N If we lose, I will be the one leaving this academy.}Đừng lo lắng. Nếu thua thì chỉ có tớ phải đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:11.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's right. This risk and pain are only mine alone.}Đúng. Đây là rủi ro và nỗi đau của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I will accept any outcome.}Dù kết quả thế nào cũng sẽ chấp nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.90,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.32,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're mistaken.}Sai rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:30.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I told you, didn't I? I want to be by your side, \N I want to be together with you more!}Tớ đã nói rồi mà? Tớ muốn được bên cạnh cậu nhiều hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.29,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This is my risk as well!}Đây là rủi ro của tớ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.75,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The question is, which card do I pick?}Câu hỏi là mình phải chọn lá nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:46.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Earlier, they figured something out.\N This means I need to look for it.}Có vẻ bọn họ đã nhận ra gì đó. Mình phải tìm ra nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.13,HorribleSubs,,0,0,650,,{D-Did you hear it? Did you hear what he said just now?}N-Này, chị có nghe anh ta tỏ tình chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Something... Some kind of hint.}Phải có gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.27,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{He noticed?}Nhận ra sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.77,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's only twenty cards left, there's no way he missed it.}Chỉ còn 20 lá, anh ấy hẳn phải nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{One card has some light smudge on it.}Có một lá có vết bẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:10.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's probably a lipstick or something similar. \N That's why it's still visible.}Đó có thể là vết son môi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:16.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Is that marked card supposed to give an advantage? No, wait.}Lá bài mang lại lợi thế tuyệt đối? Khoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:22.09,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yomozuki didn't really touch all those cards.}Yomozuki không chạm vào bất cứ lá nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It all happened back then!}Vậy hẳn là lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Which means that card is...}Tức là lá bài đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{...The Fool.}...Kẻ Khờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:34.11,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yomozuki told the truth. \N The president didn't cheat when she picked her card.}Nhưng Yumozuki cũng bảo Hội trưởng không gian lận.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:38.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And she didn't pick the card with the mark.}Và dù có gian lận nhưng chị ta cũng không lấy lá Kẻ Khờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But why did she miss it?}Tại sao lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, the reality is that card is The Fool.}Dù sao thì lá đó chính là Kẻ Khờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:51.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{All he has to do is to pick that card\N and it has to be upright!}Chỉ cần chọn lá đó là thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.05,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Picking that one?}Chọn lá đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, turn it over.}Thế lật đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No. Not this one.}Không. Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.93,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This isn't it!}Không phải nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:16.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{WHAAA? What the hell are you doing?}C-Cái gì? Anh bị điên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:20.52,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Heeey now. That's enough talking.}Nào...Im lặng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:26.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I have no idea why president left a mark on this card.}Tớ không hiểu tại sao Hội trưởng lại để dấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.13,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I know one thing.}Nhưng tớ biết rõ một điều.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:36.28,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This card might or might not be The Fool. \N For all I know, it's a big risk.}Lá này có thể là Kẻ Khờ hay không. \NNhưng nếu chọn nó tức là chấp nhận rủi ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:40.88,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You set this all up!}Cô đã nghĩ ra chuyện này
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.30,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You enjoy the risk.}vì rất thích rủi ro cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.80,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You won't leave it to anyone else!}Nên để kẻ khác chọn lấy nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.97,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But now I have the choice!}Nhưng kẻ chọn lựa là tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.71,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I decide the risk I'm going to take!}Và tôi quyết định chấp nhận rủi ro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:58.00,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This is... This is my gamble!}Đây là...Cờ bạc của tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:01.90,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{AMAZING!}QUÁ TUYỆT VỜI!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:08.65,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes, yes! Wonderful! Let's choose to leave it to fate!}Tuyệt lắm! Hãy để định mệnh quyết định hết!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.86,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You'll do this with your own hand.}Dù thế cậu vẫn có thể làm nó với đôi tay này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So...}Nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Let's gamble!}Cờ bạc điên cuồng thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:52.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And it's Judgement, upright! Plus twenty points to go Yumeko\Nresulting in twenty-one points total. It's a draw!}Lá Sự phán xét, không bị ngược! Cộng thêm\N 20 điểm cho Yumeko! Trận này hòa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:05.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{None of you will have to leave this academy.\NThat's nice. Good game, everyone!}Không ai phải rời khỏi học viện cả, tuyệt nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{President!}Hội trưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.55,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{President...}Hội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.11,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm so relieved...}May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.85,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Pull yourself together, Sayaka.}Bình tĩnh, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.37,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:37.45,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What did you do, senpai!? If you'd chosen The Fool, you would've won.\NWhy did you do such a thing?}Là sao hả? Đáng lẽ thắng rồi đó! Sao anh lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Eh... Because... I just said...}Hả...Vì...lúc nãy anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:47.38,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi, what are you rambling about?\NThere's no way that marked card was The Fool.}Sumeragi, em nói gì thế? Làm gì có chuyện dễ ăn vậy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:51.01,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Huh? But president didn't touch other cards.}Hả? Nhưng Hội trưởng chỉ chạm vào mỗi lá đó mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:20:00.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No, no. She held a few other cards in her hand. \NIf that card was The Fool, she would've picked that one for sure.}Không, không. Cô ta ép hai lá lại rồi giả bộ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:04.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No. You don't know it, Saotome-senpai.\NThat's totally a thing the president would've done.}Không, chị không biết gì về Hội trưởng cả, Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's obviously not. It's stupid.}Chả ai làm thế cả, em bị ngốc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.17,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So, wanna check it out?}Thế kiểm tra không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{As you wish.}Cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.75,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What!? Why did you do that!?}Này? Là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:15.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{As they say, the less you know the better you sleep!}Bí mật thì phải bị chôn giấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hold on! That's my...}Khoan! Đó là của tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{In the end we got a draw.}Không ngờ lại hòa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.71,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Seems like it's our destiny.}Có vẻ đây là định mệnh rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:28.63,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I feel the same! I'm sure a fun future awaits me.}Tớ cũng thế! Tương lai chắc sẽ vui lắm đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:33.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko, you do have some good servants.}Yumeko, cậu có vài nô bộc tốt đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:39.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{With them around, I'm sure it'll be more fun.}Thế này thì sẽ vui lắm đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No, they're not my servants}Không, không phải nô bộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:47.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{They are my very good friends.}Mà là những người bạn tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:01.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hello? Did you get my message?}Xin chào? Có đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:06.92,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It was great! Yumeko against the president...!}Yumeko với Hội trưởng vừa đấu với nhau! Tuyệt lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.09,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Too bad you missed it. It was very fun.}Thật tiếc khi cậu không được xem. Vui lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami Yumeko is even better than I thought.}Jabami Yumeko tuyệt hơn tớ tưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:21.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Maybe the president can't do anything about her, don't you agree?}Có lẽ Hội trưởng cũng không làm gì được cô ta. Nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Momobami Ririka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.69,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hyakkaou Private Academy.}Học viện tư thục Hyakkaou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:36.73,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Since Yumeko transferred here, \Nmany have changed because of her.}Từ khi Yumeko chuyển đến, nhiều thứ đã thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.91,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Some house pet turned human again.}Vài thú cưng đã trở lại thành người.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.71,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Someone settled an old score.}Có người đã giải quyết xong chuyện cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.57,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Someone suffered a major defeat.}Một vài người thua lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Someone began to admire her.}Có cả những người ngưỡng mộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.34,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:06.93,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And some found a new prey.}Một số thì tìm thấy con mồi mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:11.71,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I think I'll dissolve the student council.}Tôi nghĩ mình nên giải thể Hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:16.99,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But Yumeko is still the same.}Nhưng Yumeko vẫn không thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:22.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She played dozens, hunderds of games.\NBut she still keeps looking for more.}Cậu ấy chơi cả trăm ván. Nhưng vẫn chưa thỏa mãn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.93,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's not normal.}Cô ấy không phải người thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.33,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's a gambling enthusiast.}Mà là con nghiện cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:37.95,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{A compulsive gambler.}Kakegurui.
